{"sequence":40,"timestamp":"2026-04-30T04:40:18.272537579Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-f4f734a1","body":"src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_open.rs:297 only checks unstaged and untracked paths before the reset, while src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_open.rs:496 then runs `git reset --soft origin/master` and src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_open.rs:523 commits whatever is already in the index. `git reset --soft` preserves any pre-existing staged manual edits, so an operator can have a staged real-code change silently swept into the squashed PR commit even though it was not part of an `rb: checkpoint` commit. Reject or explicitly account for pre-existing staged real-code changes before the soft reset, and add a test with a staged path.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"cd0efff7781dd0291f5561533e76b42c4fc27fb088673fe73d3b3541a46177ef","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260430030405","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":41,"timestamp":"2026-04-30T04:40:18.295926671Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-4c7288e9","body":"src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_open.rs:332 builds the \"real-code\" diff stats by excluding only `.ralph-burning/**`, and src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_open.rs:606 plus src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_open.rs:615 render that list directly into the PR body and reviewer file list. That treats `.beads/issues.jsonl` and other non-source metadata as reviewer-visible real code, and it can also make src/contexts/bead_workflow/pr_open.rs:510 think there are real-code changes when only backlog metadata changed. Filter the stats/reviewer list to the stated review scope (`src/`, `tests/`, `docs/`, and config files) or explicitly exclude non-code state such as `.beads/`.","classification":"fix_current_bead","dedup_key":"9adb2219de7617d686c4bb2607fd00c5815e6c6ca3d2234b59de84d5b2f2b0aa","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.5-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260430030405","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
